Bacterial culture of strain CS2637 grown overnight was diluted 1:100 into fresh L-broth and followed by the induction of FlhD and FlhC expression by the addition of 20 mM IPTG for 2 h. Cells were collected , lysed and run in lane 5 .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=12675803" target="_blank">12675803</a>]<br></label>
